USE A PHONE?

06:36.729 --> 06:38.313
DO YOU KNOW
IT'S FREEZING OUTSIDE?

06:38.481 --> 06:39.314
AND I'M WEARING
MY UNCLE'S BOOTS,

06:39.482 --> 06:40.816
