06:40.983 --> 06:42.651
SHAGGY, SCOOBY,
WE GOT COMPANY.

06:44.695 --> 06:45.487
SO...

06:45.655 --> 06:47.155
BUDDY MORGAN.

06:47.323 --> 06:48.448
YEAH.
I KNOW YOU.

06:48.616 --> 06:50.242
YEAH. I GUESS
IT'S MY FAULT.

06:50.410 --> 06:52.285
I GAVE ERIC A RIDE HOME,
SO, UH...

06:52.453 --> 06:53.286
GET OUTTA MY CHAIR!

06:53.454 --> 06:54.329
OKAY.

06:54.497 --> 06:56.123
I REALLY HAVE TO
BE GOING ANYWAY,

06:56.290 --> 06:59.000
