IF YOU WANT.

07:04.006 --> 07:05.298
OH, YEAH. SURE.

07:05.466 --> 07:08.051
AND, HEY, GUYS, I'M REAL SORRY
I FORGOT ABOUT YA.

07:08.219 --> 07:08.927
HEY, DID YOU
WANNA DRIVE?

07:09.095 --> 07:10.303
HELL, YES!

07:12.265 --> 07:13.932
I CALL BACK SEAT.

07:16.394 --> 07:17.727
DID YOU SEE THAT?

07:17.895 --> 07:20.230
HE JUST DITCHED US
AGAIN.

07:20.982 --> 07:24.943
DO YOU EVEN KNOW HOW DIFFICULT
IT IS TO CLIQUE JUMP?

07:25.111 --> 07:27.112
