HE SEEMS NICE ENOUGH.

07:46.007 --> 07:47.841
SCREW HIM, MAN.

07:48.009 --> 07:50.552
I MEAN, HE'S GOT THE MONEY,
THE CAR, THE FAMILY.

07:50.720 --> 07:52.637
THE TEACHERS LIKE HIM.
THE COUNSELORS LIKE HIM.

07:52.805 --> 07:55.140
EVERYBODY LIKES HIM.
I HATE HIM.

07:56.142 --> 08:00.353
