SOMETHIN', OKAY?

08:03.107 --> 08:04.065
WHEN HIGH SCHOOL'S OVER,

08:04.233 --> 08:06.359
BUDDY MORGAN'S GOIN'
TO A GREAT COLLEGE.

08:06.527 --> 08:07.444
YOU KNOW WHERE I'M GONNA BE?

08:07.612 --> 08:09.988
SITTING RIGHT HERE
IN MY UNCLE'S BOOTS.

08:11.491 --> 08:14.743
