GOT GREAT FRIENDS.

08:14.911 --> 08:18.580
AND, UM, I'LL ALWAYS
BE YOUR FRIEND.

08:18.748 --> 08:20.373
THANKS, DONNA.

08:25.296 --> 08:26.713
THAT WAS SYMPATHY HYDE,

08:26.881 --> 08:29.341
