14:23.153 --> 14:24.571
WELL, WHY WOULD YOU
HAVE THOUGHT THAT?

14:24.738 --> 14:26.281
BECAUSE WE'VE BEEN SPENDING
SO MUCH TIME TOGETHER.

14:26.448 --> 14:27.615
BECAUSE WE'RE FRIENDS.

14:27.783 --> 14:30.159
I... I'VE BEEN FRIENDS
WITH HYDE FOR YEARS,

14:30.327 --> 14:31.995
AND I NEVER PUT
THE MOVES ON HIM.

14:32.162 --> 14:33.997
BUT HYDE'S A JERK.

14:34.164 --> 14:37.417
WELL, YEAH,
BUT THAT'S NOT THE REASON.

14:37.585 --> 14:39.502
IT'S BECAUSE I'M NOT GAY.

14:39.670 --> 14:41.754
RIGHT.

14:43.716 --> 14:44.924
I'M SORRY
FOR KISSING YOU.

14:45.092 --> 14:47.385
THAT'S OKAY...
I MEAN, IT'S...

14:49.638 --> 14:52.056
LET'S JUST
FORGET ABOUT IT.

14:55.269 --> 14:55.852
DO YOU WANNA LISTEN
TO THE RADIO...

14:56.020 --> 14:58.396
HEY!
I TOLD YOU I WASN'T GAY!

15:05.654 --> 15:07.030
