15:07.197 --> 15:09.324
I'M QUITTIN', KITTY.

15:11.911 --> 15:13.870
WELL, NOW,
YOU CAN'T QUIT.

15:14.038 --> 15:15.121
WHY NOT?

15:15.289 --> 15:16.456
