KEEP GOIN' LIKE THIS,

15:16.624 --> 15:19.083
BOB'S GONNA FIRE YOU, HA!

15:21.253 --> 15:23.546
IT'S A JOKE, RED.

15:24.048 --> 15:26.299
OH, I KNOW, I KNOW.
LET'S DO SOME ROLE PLAYING.

15:27.301 --> 15:28.468
WHAT?

15:28.636 --> 15:29.302
SOME ROLE PLAYING.

15:29.470 --> 15:30.720
