18:23.060 --> 18:24.977
OH, PLEASE, FEZ,
THAT'S JUST STUPID.

18:25.145 --> 18:27.688
IF BUDDY WAS GAY,
HE WOULD HAVE BEEN ALL OVER ME.

18:32.152 --> 18:34.237
WELL, HE WOULD'VE.

18:35.405 --> 18:38.032
