THE SCARY KIDS ARE GONE,

18:49.670 --> 18:51.796
IS BUDDY GAY?

18:52.923 --> 18:54.215
WELL, I DON'T THINK
IT'S REALLY MY PLACE TO...

18:54.383 --> 18:57.009
HE'S GAY.
HE'S GAY.

