LIKE, A MILLION YEARS.

19:03.142 --> 19:05.309
LET'S JUST... LET'S SAY...

19:05.477 --> 19:08.104
OKAY?

19:08.272 --> 19:09.438
THAT BUDDY...

19:09.606 --> 19:11.607
MADE A MOVE ON ME.

19:11.775 --> 19:12.859
ERIC, HE'S NOT GONNA
MAKE A MOVE ON YOU

19:13.026 --> 19:15.611
IF HE KNOWS
YOU'RE STRAIGHT.

19:16.196 --> 19:16.779
I DON'T KNOW.

19:16.947 --> 19:19.031
I MEAN, FORMAN
IS PRETTY IRRESISTIBLE.

19:21.577 --> 19:23.369
I DON'T THINK HE'LL MAKE
A MOVE ON ME AGAIN.

19:23.537 --> 19:25.496
AGAIN?
AGAIN?

19:27.291 --> 19:28.457
OR FOR THE FIRST TIME.

19:28.625 --> 19:30.668
YOU KNOW...

19:30.836 --> 19:32.670
I GOTTA GO.

19:40.137 --> 19:43.097
YOU KNOW, DONNA...

19:43.265 --> 19:45.349
IF FORMAN EVER
DECIDES TO DABBLE

19:45.517 --> 19:49.937
IN THE LOVE THAT DARE
NOT SPEAK ITS NAME,

19:50.105 --> 19:51.981
I'M HERE FOR YA.

19:56.570 --> 19:58.529
