YOUR VARIABLE SPEED HERE.

19:58.697 --> 20:00.156
IT'S COMPLETELY
STAINLESS STEEL THROUGHOUT,

20:00.324 --> 20:02.033
SO YOU KNOW
IT'LL LAST FOREVER.

20:02.201 --> 20:04.160
IT COMES WITH EVERYTHING
YOU SEE, AND, UM...

20:04.328 --> 20:05.578
SO THE ONLY DECISION
YOU'D HAVE TO MAKE

20:05.746 --> 20:06.871
IS WHAT COLOR DO YOU WANT?

20:07.039 --> 20:07.997
OH, I'LL TAKE WHITE.

20:08.165 --> 20:08.998
